verbose_text: Confirming the functional activity of these receptors, GLP-1 secretion from human organoids plated in two-dimensional cultures (XREF_FIG B) was increased by AM1638 (FFAR1 agonist, 1 muM and 10 muM), arginine vasopressin (AVP) (10 nM), angiotensin II (AngII; 10 nM), AR231453 (GPR119 agonist, 100 nM), and a GPBAR1 agonist (3 muM; XREF_FIG C).
